This paper proposes a new type of neural network, ReNN, that aims to improve interpretability and reduce the amount of data needed for optimization. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions a time-series detection problem, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY) or computer vision (cs.CV).
